data.description: Gorgeous well-kept home settled in a quiet area. This spacious home offers three bedrooms, two full bathrooms (master bath shower, hall bath jacuzzi tub), large utility room with a mud room area. This home also has an EXTRA area that is currently being used as a fourth bedroom but can easily be converted to a den. Offers a very large backyard with a wood deck for your backyard functions along with a large storage shed. Refrigerator and dishwasher to remain! The seller is willing to assist in closing costs!!!
